Package: glmmEMncv
Title: Generalized Linear Mixed Models with Nonconvex Penalties using the EM Algorithm
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Shiying", family = "Xiao",
           email = "shiying.xiao@outlook.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-8846-3258")))
Maintainer: Shiying Xiao <shiying.xiao@outlook.com>
Description: Provides a unified framework for penalized maximum likelihood
    estimation and variable selection in high-dimensional generalized linear
    mixed models. It supports multiple penalties, including lasso, SCAD, and MCP,
    and solves the resulting optimization problems efficiently using an EM
    algorithm.
